<p>Ra-Ra Raffia is the latest addition to the amazing yarn created by <a href="https://www.woolandthegang.com/">Wool And The Gang</a>, its made from 100% long wood fibre and comes in 4 beautiful natural shades.</p>

<p><img class="rounded img-fluid post-img mx-auto d-block" src="/assets/images/IMG_4743-768x768.jpeg" /></p>

<p>I‚Äôve never crocheted with raffia, it‚Äôs always been something that I felt was more suited to wrapping presents so I was very intrigued to give it a go! There are currently 8 crochet kits available, ranging from simple plant hangers to summer bags and storage baskets, all with a very summery, middle eastern vibe.</p>

<p><img class="rounded img-fluid post-img mx-auto d-block" src="/assets/images/IMG_4761-768x768.jpg" /></p>

<p>The kit I chose to try out was the ‚ÄòMoney Honey Clutch Bag‚Äô, a simple design which will make a great addition to a summer outfit (if the summer ever arrives in the UK of course!). It‚Äôs the first time I‚Äôve worked from one of WATG‚Äôs kits and I have to say how impressed I was with everything about it! Beautifully packaged in their unmistakable style it included everything you needed to make the bag ‚Äì 1 cone of Ra-Ra Raffia, money honey clutch bag crochet pattern, 3.5mm hook, darning needle and a magnetic fastening. I think it would make a perfect travelling project as everything fits neatly into the bag it comes in!</p>

<p><img class="rounded img-fluid post-img mx-auto d-block" src="/assets/images/IMG_5082-768x768.jpg" /></p>

<p>The bag was very simple to make, perfect for beginners and the raffia itself was surprisingly easy to work with. It has a suggested hook size of 4.5mm however the pattern requires a 3.5mm hook which gave the bag a more solid texture. The pattern was well written and easy to follow, the booklet also included stitch information and simple diagrams to help if required.</p>

<p><img class="rounded img-fluid post-img mx-auto d-block" src="/assets/images/IMG_5159-768x768.jpg" /></p>

<p>I‚Äôm really pleased with my finished <a href="https://www.woolandthegang.com/product/money-honey-clutch-bag/crochet-your-own">Money Honey Clutch </a>and think I will get a lot of use out of it, I loved making the bag and found the kit a pleasure to work with. Wool And The Gang products are a little more expensive than other brands but from what I have experienced you certainly get what you pay for.</p>

